What is Daily Fantasy Sports?
HOW TO PLAY


1. Sign Up
2. Buy a bidpack (and get free bids)
3. Join an available 'Contest'
4. Create your lineups
5. Double-check your lineups before the games start
6. Watch the games and contest live
7. Claim your win or join another contest

Team Battle
This is a contest between TWO futbol teams
6 Positions are available for your lineup
Captain (1) and Flex (5)
You can select any player for the FLEX or CPT position
Your CPT earns 1.5 times their fantasy points (loss or draw)
Your CPT earns 2.0 times their fantasy points if their team wins

Each player's salary will be deducted from your player budget of N50,000
Stay within your N50,000 budget to complete your lineup

Requirements:
You must select at least ONE (1) player from BOTH teams
Each user can set up to multiple lineups for each contest (if indicated)
Top "lineups" win a cash prize
This contest usually has a minimum entry for it to run
This contest also has a maximum entry for the prize pool
[current entries]/[minimum entries]/[maximum entries]
e.g. 0/6/12
Once the minimum requirements are met
[current entries]/[maximum entries] e.g. 6/12

Entry Cost
5 or 10 Real Bids are required to enter a TB 100k or 10k contest
10 or 20 Real Bids are required to enter a TB 200k or 20k contest
20 or 40 Real Bids are required to enter a TB 400k or 40 contest

×
League Battle
This is a contest that happens when 2 or more games are available at the same time slot
8 Positions are available for your lineup
Forwards (2)
Midfielders (2)
Defense (2)
Goalkeeper (1)
Util (F/M/D) (1)
You can select any F/M/D for the UTIL position
Each player's salary will be deducted from your player budget of N50,000
Stay within your N50,000 budget to complete your lineup

Requirements:
You must select players from at least THREE (3) teams
Each user can set up to multiple lineups for each contest (if indicated)
Top "lineups" win a cash prize
This contest usually has a minimum entry for it to run
This contest also has a maximum entry for the prize pool
[current entries]/[minimum entries]/[maximum entries]
e.g. 0/12/24
Once the minimum requirements are met
[current entries]/[maximum entries] e.g. 12/24

Entry Cost
5 or 10 Real Bids are required to enter a LB 100k or 10k contest
10 or 20 Real Bids are required to enter a LB 200k or 20k contest
20 or 40 Real Bids are required to enter a LB 400k or 40 contest
